1
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:41,170
Lu Danyu,

2
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:42,520
wake up.

3
00:00:43,160 --> 00:00:44,880
The Son of the World is in danger.

4
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,680
What's wrong?

5
00:00:46,200 --> 00:00:49,060
Yue Qi, who you met during the day, is a flower demon.

6
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:50,120
What?

7
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:52,400
She is in the Son of the World's room.

8
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:54,120
I sensed the fluctuation of demonic power.

9
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:54,600
Hurry.

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:58,000
Is a midnight sneak attack really how demons operate?

11
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,690
Where are you going?

12
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,720
Why are you here?

13
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,040
This is my room.

14
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,640
Why am I here?

15
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,780
I'm going to the restroom.

16
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,600
Yiyi.

17
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,400
I don't know how to do anything.

18
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,520
Will it help if I go?

19
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,320
Won't I just be dying with him?

20
00:01:20,680 --> 00:01:21,880
Demons hidden in the human world

21
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,610
usually don't make a big scene.

22
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,000
As long as you wake up the Son of the World,

23
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,240
she should leave.

24
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:29,970
Brother Wuzhou.

25
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,850
Open the door, Brother Wuzhou.

26
00:01:31,880 --> 00:01:32,960
Are you in there?

27
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,130
Open the door, Brother Wuzhou.

28
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,610
Brother Wuzhou.

29
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,920
Open the door, Brother Wuzhou.

30
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,000
She's gone.

31
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,560
She just left?

32
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:45,080
I thought she was supposed to be a powerful figure.

33
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,360
Yiyi.

34
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,600
Yiyi.

35
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:52,500
It seems Yiyi is really out of energy.

36
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,660
She fell asleep without saying a word this time.

37
00:01:58,360 --> 00:01:59,560
What's wrong, Danyu?

38
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,760
What happened?

39
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,220
Why are you in such a hurry?

40
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,530
Didn't you say you were going to the bathroom?

41
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,160
What?

42
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,760
She's going to the bathroom?

43
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,720
How did you know?

44
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:21,640
I meant,

45
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,600
I was going to wake my brother up to go to the bathroom.

46
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,060
Ah, yes.

47
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:24,960
Brother Wuzhou.

48
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,040
You've been holding it for a long time, haven't you?

49
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:28,240
I came to wake you up to use the bathroom.

50
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:28,960
Danyu.

51
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,820
You came to wake me up for that?

52
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:32,760
Danyu.

53
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,400
You told him

54
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,320
you were coming to wake me up?

55
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,600
You and him...

56
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,079
Liyuan!

57
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,520
Did you go to my sister's room again?

58
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:49,600
It was clearly your sister who came to my room.

59
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:49,920
You!

60
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,720
No, no, no.

61
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,200
Brother, he's talking nonsense.

62
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,280
I didn't go to any other room.

63
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,320
I was in my own room.

64
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:55,960
Really?

65
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,170
Really, really.

66
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,050
Nothing is truer than my words.

67
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,640
Since I've already woken you up,

68
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,770
my task is complete.

69
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,570
I'm leaving.

70
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,240
Danyu!

71
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,120
Danyu!

72
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,940
Why did you close the door?

73
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,480
I have to go to the restroom.

74
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,800
Danyu.

75
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,640
Danyu.

76
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,690
Brother Wuzhou,

77
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:45,240
what are you doing at Liyuan's door?

78
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,970
I didn't peek at him.

79
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,200
I was just passing by.

80
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,250
Just passing by.

81
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,960
What are you doing at my door?

82
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,160
I...

83
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,700
came to wake you up.

84
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,120
It's time for breakfast.

85
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,410
Why are you the one waking me up?

86
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,690
Where is Mu Chenxue?

87
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,520
Is Xiaoxue your servant?

88
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,610
Why must she wake you up every time?

89
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,960
Because he likes Sister Mu.

90
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,690
You're all here.

91
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,880
Everyone's gathered.

92
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,740
Have you eaten?

93
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,440
Not yet.

94
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,280
We just got up too, Sister Mu.

95
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,040
You guys eat first.

96
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,300
I'm going out for a bit.

97
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,940
Xiaoxue, where are you going?

98
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,880
I want to go out and see

99
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,320
if there are any fresh herbs.

100
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,520
Then I'll go with you.

101
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,480
Okay.

102
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,159
Danyu,

103
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,100
we're leaving.

104
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,240
Sir,

105
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,050
were these herbs

106
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,280
just picked?

107
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,480
Of course.

108
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,159
They were picked

109
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,960
this morning.

110
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,280
I was afraid they would lose their spiritual energy,

111
00:04:58,280 --> 00:04:59,680
so I didn't dare clean them up.

112
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,520
I hurried over here

113
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,120
to wait for the destined one.

114
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,770
Xiaoxue,

115
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:03,720
he said

116
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,200
you're the destined one.

117
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,560
We came over as soon as we saw him.

118
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,420
It must be fate.

119
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,320
Then we should

120
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,380
pick out a few more.

121
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,320
Go ahead.

122
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,860
Pick some more.

123
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,200
I'll give you a discount.

124
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:17,860
A discount.

125
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,620
How about this one?

126
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:44,960
You are not him.

127
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:03,760
Sir.

128
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,050
This is too much.

129
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:06,880
This spirit stone,

130
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,280
I can't make change for it.

131
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,210
Keep the change.

132
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,000
You can have this spirit stone.

133
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,520
What are you two doing?

134
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:13,920
I have hands and feet

135
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:15,480
and can earn my own living.

136
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,080
How could I

137
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,360
take other people's money for nothing?

138
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,280
True.

139
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,880
This old gentleman is of noble character.

140
00:06:21,880 --> 00:06:23,810
How could I measure him with money?

141
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:27,360
What an interesting kid.

142
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:29,680
I am

143
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,880
not exactly of noble character.

144
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,640
I just

145
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,570
don't want to take money from a kid.

146
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:35,960
By the way,

147
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:36,360
you

148
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,770
aren't locals, are you?

149
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:38,760
Sir,

150
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,980
you have a good eye.

151
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:43,120
It's not that I have a good eye.

152
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,400
It's just that

153
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,640
you are too different

154
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,320
from the locals.

155
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,320
These days,

156
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,360
everyone is having a hard time.

157
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,480
In this world,

158
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,360
spiritual energy is gradually withering,

159
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,220
plunging the people into misery.

160
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,600
Just being able to feed oneself

161
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,080
is good enough.

162
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,180
The residents of this city

163
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,920
no longer have

164
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,040
such clear eyes like yours.

165
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:07,680
Especially...

166
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:09,760
Sir,

167
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,880
what's wrong?

168
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,940
Is there something you can't say?

169
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,600
If you

170
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,940
aren't planning to

171
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,640
stay here for a long time,

172
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,320
you'd better leave quickly.

173
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:19,040
In this city,

174
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,040
there are monsters harming people.

175
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,640
Monsters?

176
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,080
For thirty years,

177
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:29,210
no one has been able to subdue them.

178
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:46,300
You are the one from last time.

179
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,530
I pay my respects to you, Fairy.

180
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:50,370
Why are you here?

181
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:52,640
I

182
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:55,520
had a connection with the young master long ago,

183
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,180
even earlier than you, Fairy.

184
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:58,080
Therefore,

185
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,720
I hope you can step aside.

186
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,480
In matters of love,

187
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,740
how can one step aside?

188
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:05,890
Besides,

189
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,120
how can you prove

190
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,780
that you knew him before I did?

191
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,680
Fairy,

192
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,930
just come with me and you will know.

193
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,130
Where to?

194
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,760
After you.

195
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,360
No.

196
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:29,220
I can't find her anywhere.

197
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:31,820
I searched the whole inn, but she's not here.

198
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,919
Brother Wuzhou.

199
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:34,720
What's wrong?

200
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,400
How is this possible?

201
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,240
How could Xiaoxue go missing?

202
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:41,919
Danyu.

203
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,120
What?

204
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,640
Sister Mu is missing?

205
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,240
Danyu.

206
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:50,280
Tell me.

207
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:52,400
Xiaoxue is unfamiliar with this place.

208
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,460
Where could she go?

209
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,440
Brother Wuzhou.

210
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,360
Don't panic just yet.

211
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,090
Let's split up and look for her.

212
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:57,560
Right.

213
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,760
Let's go look.

214
00:08:58,960 --> 00:08:59,360
Right.

215
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,040
Hurry up.

216
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,600
You can't rush when looking for someone.

217
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,000
The more anxious you are, the messier it gets.

218
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,120
And the harder it is to find them.

219
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,600
Xiaoxue!

220
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,500
What happened?

221
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:14,680
How did you get hurt like this?
